Scott: Monitors for your computer.

256
00:17:22,520 --> 00:17:28,319
Rym: Which basically boils down to CRTs, cathode ray tubes, or LCDs, liquid crystal displays.

257
00:17:29,640 --> 00:17:34,280
Rym: Now it just so happens that Scott knows quite a bit about the latter and I know quite a bit about the former.

258
00:17:34,980 --> 00:17:39,718
